g>回想房</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >除了精美 CG，遊戲中還能隨時重溫兩位可愛女主角的火辣場景，想看幾次都可以！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>", "short_description": "化身美麗且懷抱野心的鍊金術師拉皮絲・費露西亞，探索世界、完成任務、討伐魔物、收集珍稀素材，鍊製世上最稀有之物！不惜一切代價，助她成為頂尖鍊金術師！", "supported_languages": "英文, 日文<strong>*</strong>, 簡體中文, 繁體中文<br><strong>*</strong>具備完整音效支援的語言", "header_image": "https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3741440/21f7aa2b50f0763090cee58ee9c9fd3c3f6fa221/header.jpg?t=1755276523", "capsule_image": "https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3741440/09dc2124db6eccb67fe9925a29d86c0a2472bd66/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1755276523", "capsule_imagev5": "https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3741440/09dc2124db6eccb67fe9925a29d86c0a2472bd66/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1755276523", "website": "https://saikeystudios.com", "pc_requirements": {"minimum": "<strong>最低配備:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>作業系統 *:</strong> Windows® 7/8/8.1/10<br></li><li><strong>處理器:</strong> Intel Core2 Duo or better<br></li><li><strong>記憶體:</strong> 4 GB 記憶體<br></li><li><strong>顯示卡:</strong> DirectX 9/OpenGL 4.1 capable GPU<br></li><li><strong>儲存空間:</strong> 2 GB 可用空間</li></ul>"}, "mac_requirements": [], "linux_requirements": [], "legal_notice": "2025 Saikey Studios", "release_date": {"coming_soon": true, "date": "即將推出"}}}}